  <brief_title>Prevention of Preterm Labor in Patients With a Previous Episode of Threatened Preterm Labor With Progesterone</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of 17α Hydroxyprogesterone Caproate for the Prevention of Preterm Labor in Patients With a Previous Episode of Threatened Preterm Labor During Current Pregnancy. Double Blind, Randomized, Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
