  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women between 26 and 34 weeks of gestation.

          -  Cervical length (determined by transvaginal ultrasound) below the 10th percentile for
             the gestational age.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Multiple gestations.

          -  Maternal pathologies in which preterm termination of pregnancy is required.
      </textblock>
